{"title":"About","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"About"},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\nThis website is a portfolio of the work I want to share, the various ramblings of what I've learned or things I needed to reference again later, and a website to share who I am with whoever in interested.\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"resume-section\">\n  <h2>Experience</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">Statistical Consultant</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">2024 – Present</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University Statistical Consulting Center</div>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Led statistical analyses across 20+ interdisciplinary projects spanning environmental science, healthcare, and social work.</li>\n      <li>Designed simulation studies and statistical models to evaluate complex experimental data.</li>\n      <li>Collaborated with domain experts to translate analytical results into actionable insights.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">Research Assistant</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">2025 - Present</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Eli Lilly (Contract)</div>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Developed anomaly detection methods for clinical trial monitoring systems.</li>\n      <li>Built machine learning pipelines for identifying under-reporting in clinical sites.</li>\n      <li>Improved uncertainty quantification for decision-making workflows.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">Teaching Assistant</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">2022 - 2024</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University Department of Statistical Science</div>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Supported undergraduate and graduate statistics courses through instruction, grading, and individualized assistance</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Education</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">Ph.D in Statistics</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">Expected Aug 2026</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">M.S. in Statistics</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">Dec 2023</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">B.S. in Statistics</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">May 2022</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2> Let's Connect! </h2>\n</div>\n\n```\n\n<div class=\"social-buttons\">\n\n  <a href=\"https://linkedin.com/in/nathen-byford\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"social-btn linkedin\">\n    <i class=\"bi bi-linkedin\"></i> LinkedIn\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/nathenbyford\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"social-btn github\">\n    <i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i> GitHub\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"mailto:nate@natebyford.com\" class=\"social-btn email\">\n    <i class=\"bi bi-envelope\"></i> Email\n  </a>\n\n</div>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\nThis website is a portfolio of the work I want to share, the various ramblings of what I've learned or things I needed to reference again later, and a website to share who I am with whoever in interested.\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"resume-section\">\n  <h2>Experience</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"resume-item\">\n    <div class=\"resume-header\">\n      <span class=\"role\">Statistical Consultant</span>\n      <span class=\"date\">2024 – Present</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"organization\">Baylor University Statistical Consulting Center</div>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Led statistical analyses across 20+ interdisciplinary projects spanning environmental science, healthcare, a